title: Shoot the Boot - Oystein Braten
description:
The first #UNREASONABLE winner is our team rider Øystein Braten! He is now in contention to win the boot at the end of the Nine Knights event. Check it out here - needless to say, don't try this at home.

O'Neill has brought our top riders and skiers to Livignio, Italy, for the Nine Knights event. Each day we will release an edit of the event's most unreasonable moments. Winner takes all.
